<i>noun</i>: 조정 [조정], 적응 [저긍], 순응 [수ː능], 가감 [가감] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>조정 [조정]</dt><br>
<dd>adjustment; change</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 기준이나 상황에 맞게 바로잡아 정리함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of correcting and adjusting in accordance with a certain standard or circumstances.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>적응 [저긍]</dt><br>
<dd>adaptation; adjustment</dd><br>
<dd>어떠한 조건이나 환경에 익숙해지거나 알맞게 변화함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of getting accustomed to, or changing to fit into, a condition or environment.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>순응 [수ː능]</dt><br>
<dd>adaptation; adjustment</dd><br>
<dd>환경이나 변화에 알맞게 되어 익숙해지거나 체계, 명령 등에 순순히 따름.</dd><br>
<dd>The state or act of getting used to an environment or change, or obediently following a system, order, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가감 [가감]</dt><br>
<dd>addition and subtraction; adjustment</dd><br>
<dd>더하거나 뺌.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of adding or subtracting.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>